Title: [BOUNTY][ICO] ValueCash - CRYPTOCURRENCY REFORMATION BEYOND LIMITS | [ENDED]
Body: ValueCash is giving 200,000 XVL Tokens through a variety of Bounty Campaigns.  NOTE: To participate in any of the bounty campaign, you MUST sign up at ValueCash website HERE to receive your tokens in your ValueCash back-office after ICO ends. ValueCash is not based on ERC20 smart token, so no need to post your ETH address here on the thread.  Weekly Allocation will take place throughout the below-mentioned dates: Week 1 - February 6, 2018 - February 12, 2018 Week 2 - February 13, 2018 - February 19, 2018 Week 3 - February 20, 2018 - February 26, 2018 Week 4 -  February 27, 2018 - March 5, 2018         Week 5 - March 6, 2018 - March 12, 2018 Week 6 - March 13, 2018 - March 19, 2018  Bounty Allocation: Airdrop - 20% [Link - https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2915195.0] Signature & Avatar Campaign  - 15% [Link - https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2984149.0] Translation Campaign – 12% Articles & Blogs Campaign – 15% Facebook Campaign – 15% Twitter Campaign – 15% YouTube Campaign – 5% YouTube Campaign (2) - 3%    We need people to help translate and moderate our ANN Thread and our WhitePaper.  Rules One reservation for each language and don’t use Google Translate. Quality Translations are expected, as well, don’t make it a dead-horse. You need to moderate it till the end of bounty, else no rewards. Should update ANN Thread with all the latest stuff posted by ValueCash team which can be found here. Moderators are required to keep the local thread alive. Must ensure questions asked on the thread are answered accordingly. Minimum of 2 posts (100+ characters) per week, in the translated language thread. A single post thread will be rejected. We require translators to translate ANN Thread and whitepaper in a max period of 2 weeks. Failing to do so (and if found to be using Google Translate) will result in their stakes being forfeited and other translator will be given the opportunity.  Rewards ANN thread translation+moderation - 15 Stakes Whitepaper Translation: 10 Stakes  Languages needed Spanish - Icoservices2018 (DONE) Italian Chinese Dutch Hindi German French - Tospik (DONE) Korean Russian - speaknow (DONE) Japanese - HongKong (DONE)  Links for ANN and Whitepaper Files given below: ANN - https://drive.google.com/file/d/15AaBuidC41OM0fNFq5Dib0FFBFXPVjsE/view?usp=drive_web Whitepaper - https://docs.google.com/viewer?url=http%3A%2F%2Fvaluecash.com%2Fpublic%2Fassets%2Ffiles%2FWhitepaper.pdf  How to participate Fill the Translation bounty form here: https://valuecash.com/bounty/translation Check your status on the spreadsheet here - https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1INy2utkGah_nKoS2hDxJLza21d1hH7MJHKnHvRf-TOA/edit#gid=1139725289     Rules Article/Blog Post needs to contain at least 300 words.
